data.title: Haylie duff & Nick Zano house hunt!
data.meta_description: Wearing a colorful scarf, Ugg boots and her hair up in a high ponytail, Haylie Duff ventured out with her new boyfriend Nick Zano to go house shopping together on Saturday afternoon (April 19). The cute couple, along with a real estate agent, stopped at several houses in the Toluca Lake…
